Title: Yankee White
Plot: While on Air Force One, a Navy commanding officer dies.  Agents from the Navy NCIS decide to take the investigation into their own hands and also force a Secret Service Agent to help.  Now the NCIS team has to figure out if the Navy Officer's death was of natural causes or not.
GuestStars: Gerry Becker, Joe Spano, Gary Grubbs, Lawrence Pressman, Gregory Itzin, Dane Northcutt, Gerald Downey, Robert Bagnell, Gerald McCullouch, Pancho Demmings, Alan Dale
